:

*Borbi* se nastavljaju (The fights continue).
On je bio žestok *borba* (He was a fierce fight).
Oni su se sukobili u *borbi* (They clashed in the fight).
Njihova *borba* je bila duga i teška (Their fight was long and hard).
Ona je tražila da uđe u *borbu* (She asked to enter the fight).
Njihove *borbe* su bile gotovo neprekidne (Their fights were almost continuous).